Background

		Mr. Stephen W. Bershad served as the Chief Executive Officer and Chairman of the Board of General Dynamics Global Imaging Technologies, Inc. since 1986. Mr. Bershad served as the Managing Director of Lehman Brothers Inc., and its predecessor firms, where he held series of senior management positions in merchant banking and mergers and acquisitions. Mr. Bershad has been the Chairman of Novanta Inc. (alternate name: GSI Group Inc.) since July 30, 2010 and EMCOR Group Inc. ... since June 13, 2013. He served as a Lead Director for Emcor Group Inc. from May 2012 to June 13, 2013. Mr. Bershad has been a Director of Axsys Technologies, Inc. since 1986 and Independent Director of EMCOR Group Inc. since December 15, 1994.Read Full Background




