Mr. Stephen W. Bershad is Chairman at GSI Group, Inc. and Chairman at EMCOR Group, Inc.
Mr. Bershad was previously employed as Chairman & Chief Executive Officer by Axsys Technologies, Inc. and a Managing Director by Lehman Brothers, Inc.
